      "instruction": "<p>While the pepper is cooking, add your<strong> bulgur wheat </strong>to a pot with plenty of <strong>boiled water </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 7-9 min or until tender with a slight bite</p><p>Once cooked, drain and return to the pot</p>",
