    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and roughly chop your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Strip your <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them roughly, discard the stems</p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley </strong>finely, including the stems</p><p>Cut your <strong>halloumi</strong> into 3 slices per person</p><p>Slice your<strong> lemon[s]</strong> in half</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
