    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>halloumi</strong> and cook for 2-3 min on each side or until golden</p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Ordered extra halloumi? Slice and cook in a pan with a little oil for 4-6 min or until golden all over</span></strong></p>",
