    {
      "instruction": "<p>Fluff the cooked, drained <strong>bulgur</strong> <strong>wheat</strong> with a fork</p><p>Add the juice of the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> and <strong>half</strong> of the<strong> chopped herbs </strong>(save the rest for garnish!)</p><p>Season with <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your<strong> herby bulgur</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> salad</strong>, then pat dry with<strong> </strong>kitchen paper</p>",
