    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>herby bulgur </strong>with the <strong>salad </strong>and <strong>muhammara dip </strong>to the side</p><p>Tip: Use the back of a spoon to spread the dip on the plate</p><p>Top with the<strong> golden</strong> <strong>halloumi</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining chopped herbs </strong>and <strong>walnuts </strong>and drizzle everything with a little <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
